:viewButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/question.handbook
View

The View button menu provides choices for
following hypertext links, for obtaining
information about the currently displayed page,
and for adjusting and magnifying the page
display.

Follow Link: 

	To follow a hypertext link, first 
	click SELECT on a link on the current 
	page and then choose Follow Link.

Standard Magnification:

	Magnification returns to the default
	value (100%0 for the Help handbook page
	layout.
	
Custom Magnification:

	Provides a slider for you to set your
	own magnification value for the Help
	Viewer page.
	

