:magnifyPanel:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/question.handbook
Custom Magnification

Hold down SELECT to drag the slider to
the desired numeric value (displayed
in the Magnification Percentage field).

Click SELECT on either side of the
slider control to increase or decrease
magnification in increments of 1%.

Then click SELECT on Apply (to set the
new magnification) or Reset (to return
to the previous setting).

:magnifySlider:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/question.handbook
Magnify Slider

Hold down SELECT and drag the slider to
set the Magnification Percentage.

Click SELECT on either side of the
slider control to increase or decrease
magnification in increments of 1%.

Click SELECT on Apply (to set the
new magnification) or Reset (to return
to the previous setting).

############50_Characters#########################
:applyButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/question.handbook
Apply

Click SELECT on the Apply button to set the
page magnification according to its value
on the slider.

#
:resetButton:$OPENWINHOME/bin/helpopen handbooks/question.handbook
Reset

Click SELECT on Reset to revert to the previous 
page magnification setting.
